<DOCHDR>
http://www.savers.org:80/claremont/edit/2budgets.htm 204.71.237.73 19970108010228 text/html 5608
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 01:02:43 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 07-Jan-97 08:10:50 GMT
Content-length: 5421
