<DOCNO>WT16-B30-41</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA022-000236-B025-129</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.savers.org:80/claremont/gsp/gsp49.htm 204.71.237.73 19970108011223 text/html 70990
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
