<H2>Edited by John A. Baden</H2>
<H3>Published by Pacific Research Institute for Public Policy</H3>

<FONT SIZE =3>
<P>San Francisco, CA</P>
<IMG ALIGN="TOP" SRC="/free/Images/egore.gif" WIDTH=50%>
