http://www.savers.org:80/mrc/nq/95nq18.html 204.71.237.73 19970108015405 text/html 7975
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 01:54:11 GMT
